title: Cries from Syria (2017 Documentary)
description:
==== Cries from Syria ====

Syrian activists, revolutionary leaders, former army generals, journalists and ordinary citizens discuss their country's humanitarian crisis and civil war.


Initial release: 2017
Director: Evgeny Afineevsky
Music composed by: Martin Tillman
Producers: Evgeny Afineevsky, Den Tolmor, Aaron Butler
Cinematography: Evgeny Afineevsky, Faris Al-Shawaf, more
Executive producers: Sheila Nevins, Lara Alameddine, Daniel Dubiecki, David Dinerstein

==========================

Since I haven't seen any releases of the doc yet, I decided to post it myself
It's strong come with an open mind
